title: Why does Catalonia want to become independent?
description:
Have you heard of a place called Catalonia?
The debate is about whether Catalonia should become independent from Spain. I'm Catalan by birth and I believe that, for somebody who is not, it can be quite difficult to understand why we want independence. That's why I decided to explain some of these reasons.

Has sentit a parlar mai d'un lloc anomenat Catalunya?
Sobre la taula hi ha el debat sobre si Catalunya s'hauria d'independitzar d'Espanya. Sóc catalana de naixement i crec que, per algú que no ho és, pot ser difícil d'entendre perquè volem l'independència. Per això vaig decidir explicar algunes de les raons.
